comments: Portis (WAS) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and disengage in the lane.
RAR shows Rubio (UTA) moves laterally into McRae's (WAS) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.  After the illegal action, McRae makes inadvertent contact to Rubio's face.
Gobert (UTA) extends his backside into McRae (WAS) during the pick and pushes him, affecting his ability to defend the play.
Portis (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Ingles' (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Beal's (WAS) path and does not deliver contact.
During the pick, Beal (WAS) briefly grasps Mitchell's (UTA) arm but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Portis (WAS) delivers contact to Ingles (UTA) and dislodges him from his defensive position.
Portis (WAS) sets the pick on Ingles (UTA) and moves into him, affecting his ability to defend the play.
Crowder (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Beal's (WAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Beal (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Mitchell (UTA) and makes incidental contact that does not affect his SQBR or ability to make the pass.
Gobert (UTA) makes incidental contact with Portis's (WAS) arm that does not affect his ability to secure the rebound.
Ingles (UTA) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Beal (WAS).
Parker (WAS) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
Rubio (UTA) makes incidental contact to the arm of McRae (WAS) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Crowder (UTA) makes incidental contact with Beal (WAS) as he attempts to go for the rebound.
Gobert (UTA) makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) arm that does not affect his ability to make the pass.
Brown Jr. (WAS) commits a take foul on Rubio (UTA).
Portis (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Parker (WAS) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (UTA) path and does not deliver contact.
Gobert (UTA) makes incidental body contact with McRae (WAS) after cleanly blocking the shot attempt.
